20.9712 	EXP 	txt_resFileClashWarn: text = 'Task: FDOT_140222\n\nParticipant ID: 1\nSession: 1 \n\n\nAVISO: Já existem ficheiros para esta versão da experiência e participante\n\nAll results files have a unique timestamp, but this data will have the same participant and session identifiers as an existing data set.\n\nDo you want to continue with the entered participant & session information? \n\n\n[Researcher: Press Y to CONTINUE, press N to QUIT]'
